<H1>Algebraic groups over finite fields, a quick proof of Lang's
theorem</H1>

<P>

We give an easy proof of Lang's theorem about the surjectivity of the
Lang map <I>g --> g<SUP>-1</SUP>F(g)</I> on a linear algebraic group defined
over a finite field, where <I>F</I> is a Frobenius endomorphism.

